-- Yahoo CEO says rolling out new management structure
-- 
-- Thu Feb 26, 2009 1:11pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/02/26/us-yahoo-structure-sb-idUSTRE51P60Z20090226

 

 (Reuters) - Yahoo Inc CEO Carol Bartz said on Thursday the company is "rolling out a new management structure." 

 Bartz said the reorganization will to help make speedier decisions, eliminate "silos," and focus on the customer.